headline: ROLLINS, INC. ANNOUNCES NOMINATION OF PAUL D. DONAHUE TO STAND FOR ELECTION TO BOARD OF DIRECTORS AT 2025 ANNUAL MEETING
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE: ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, announced that Paul D. Donahue has been nominated by the Board of Directors (the "Board") to stand for election to the Board at the upcoming 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders (the "Annual Meeting").
